Pachube JS Widgets
==================

Usage:

  In your page include:

    <head>
      <script src="http://www.pachube.com/widgets/pbloader.js"></script>
    </head>

    <body>
      <!-- For each graph you want, include: -->
      <div id="graph" class="pachube-graph" pachube-resource="feeds/FEED_ID/datastreams/DATASTREAM_ID" pachube-key="API_KEY" style="width:WIDTH; height:HEIGHT;">&nbsp;</div>
    </body>

Options:
  Optional settings you can use to set up your graph include:
    static          Ensures the graph is always centered
                    around the current timespan.
                    (i.e. Midnight-to-Midnight, or Hour-to-Hour)

    update="auto"   Automatically updates the graph with
                    new data every 5 minutes.
